We enclose the following:
1. Audited Financial Results Segment Reporting Statement of Cash Flows and Statement of Assets & Liabilities for
the Quarter and Year ended March 31 2025;
2. Audit Report issued by the Statutory Auditors for the Quarter and Year ended March 31 2025;
3. Declaration confirming that Auditors has issued unmodified opinion with respect to the Audited Financial
Results for the quarter/ year ended March 31 2025.

